   <text>
      <body>
         <div>

            <p>
                    <seg corresp="#KR2p0085_tls_001-1a.1" xml:lang="en">The old Duke met in Lu with Great Duke Wang, </seg>
               <seg corresp="#KR2p0085_tls_001-1a.2" xml:lang="en">then said: </seg>
               <seg corresp="#KR2p0085_tls_001-1a.3" xml:lang="en">I have heard that the clan of Zhou has problems, </seg>
               <seg corresp="#KR2p0085_tls_001-1a.4" xml:lang="en">and does not [...] </seg>
               <seg corresp="#KR2p0085_tls_001-1a.5" xml:lang="en">I have heard of the luminous clan. </seg>
               <seg corresp="#KR2p0085_tls_001-1a.6" xml:lang="en">The old Duke [...] </seg>
               <seg corresp="#KR2p0085_tls_001-1a.7" xml:lang="en"> </seg>
                </p>

            <p>
                    <seg corresp="#KR2p0085_tls_001-2a.1" xml:lang="en">you have already felt shame because of this, </seg>
               <seg corresp="#KR2p0085_tls_001-2a.2" xml:lang="en">and the right or wrong of it will be known. </seg>
               <seg corresp="#KR2p0085_tls_001-2a.3" xml:lang="en">The old Duke [...] </seg>
               <seg corresp="#KR2p0085_tls_001-2a.4" xml:lang="en"> </seg>
                </p>

            <p>
                    <seg corresp="#KR2p0085_tls_001-3a.1" xml:lang="en">King Wen asked the august father about government. </seg>
               <seg corresp="#KR2p0085_tls_001-3a.2" xml:lang="en">King Wen said: </seg>
               <seg corresp="#KR2p0085_tls_001-3a.3" xml:lang="en">If I obtain the august father ('s help), </seg>
               <seg corresp="#KR2p0085_tls_001-3a.4" xml:lang="en">I will carry (?) all under Heaven. </seg>
               <seg corresp="#KR2p0085_tls_001-3a.5" xml:lang="en">If I lose the august father ('s help), </seg>
               <seg corresp="#KR2p0085_tls_001-3a.6" xml:lang="en">then my people, the Zhou, will be in fear. </seg>
               <seg corresp="#KR2p0085_tls_001-3a.7" xml:lang="en">Once he had spoken, the august father then advanced (?) </seg>
               <seg corresp="#KR2p0085_tls_001-3a.8" xml:lang="en"> </seg>
                </p>

            <p>
                    <seg corresp="#KR2p0085_tls_001-4a.1" xml:lang="en">In the seventh year (?), </seg>
               <seg corresp="#KR2p0085_tls_001-4a.2" xml:lang="en">King Wen asked the august father: </seg>
               <seg corresp="#KR2p0085_tls_001-4a.3" xml:lang="en">saying: </seg>
               <seg corresp="#KR2p0085_tls_001-4a.4" xml:lang="en">I am troubled on all sides, </seg>
               <seg corresp="#KR2p0085_tls_001-4a.5" xml:lang="en">I want to reach balance and hold the proper way </seg>
               <seg corresp="#KR2p0085_tls_001-4a.6" xml:lang="en">In the past we (the old rulers of Zhou) obtained balance, </seg>
               <seg corresp="#KR2p0085_tls_001-4a.7" xml:lang="en">and had no regrets generation after generation. </seg>
                </p>

            <p>
                    <seg corresp="#KR2p0085_tls_001-5a.1" xml:lang="en">Even if a method is practiced [=if the government is not in chaos]), </seg>
               <seg corresp="#KR2p0085_tls_001-5a.2" xml:lang="en">if it is not something that Heaven favors, </seg>
               <seg corresp="#KR2p0085_tls_001-5a.3" xml:lang="en">nobody can achieve it; </seg>
               <seg corresp="#KR2p0085_tls_001-5a.4" xml:lang="en">when one retreats and examines it, </seg>
               <seg corresp="#KR2p0085_tls_001-5a.5" xml:lang="en">how could they be worthy people? [=the ones that make such wrong choices] </seg>
                </p>

            <p>
                    <seg corresp="#KR2p0085_tls_001-6a.1" xml:lang="en">Your guidance, </seg>
               <seg corresp="#KR2p0085_tls_001-6a.2" xml:lang="en">I am unable to attain it, </seg>
               <seg corresp="#KR2p0085_tls_001-6a.3" xml:lang="en">and yet I continuously carry it on (?) </seg>
               <seg corresp="#KR2p0085_tls_001-6a.4" xml:lang="en">Now, establishing a functioning society (?), </seg>
               <seg corresp="#KR2p0085_tls_001-6a.5" xml:lang="en">(this) is what is most difficult to achieve under Heaven. </seg>
               <seg corresp="#KR2p0085_tls_001-6a.6" xml:lang="en">Some rise because of it, </seg>
               <seg corresp="#KR2p0085_tls_001-6a.7" xml:lang="en">some decay, </seg>
               <seg corresp="#KR2p0085_tls_001-6a.8" xml:lang="en">the duke should bring it to completion. (?) </seg>
                </p>

            <p>
                    <seg corresp="#KR2p0085_tls_001-7a.1" xml:lang="en">Now examining what is below (?), </seg>
               <seg corresp="#KR2p0085_tls_001-7a.2" xml:lang="en">he talked about the ancestors of the Zhou people: </seg>
               <seg corresp="#KR2p0085_tls_001-7a.3" xml:lang="en">What Heaven favors, </seg>
               <seg corresp="#KR2p0085_tls_001-7a.4" xml:lang="en">one should second; </seg>
               <seg corresp="#KR2p0085_tls_001-7a.5" xml:lang="en">what heaven opposes, </seg>
               <seg corresp="#KR2p0085_tls_001-7a.6" xml:lang="en">one should reject; </seg>
               <seg corresp="#KR2p0085_tls_001-7a.7" xml:lang="en">Among creatures, there are the ones to follow, </seg>
               <seg corresp="#KR2p0085_tls_001-7a.8" xml:lang="en">this is not the Heaven's child's work [=something that you can modify?) </seg>
                </p>

            <p>
                    <seg corresp="#KR2p0085_tls_001-8a.1" xml:lang="en">He asked to (meet?) privately with the master. </seg>
               <seg corresp="#KR2p0085_tls_001-8a.2" xml:lang="en">In the past, Shun with great [...] </seg>
               <seg corresp="#KR2p0085_tls_001-8a.3" xml:lang="en">[...] then left. </seg>
               <seg corresp="#KR2p0085_tls_001-8a.4" xml:lang="en">Since they met (?) </seg>
               <seg corresp="#KR2p0085_tls_001-8a.5" xml:lang="en">he will come back (?), </seg>
               <seg corresp="#KR2p0085_tls_001-8a.6" xml:lang="en">and then King Wen [...] </seg>
               <seg corresp="#KR2p0085_tls_001-8a.7" xml:lang="en"> </seg>
                </p>

            <p>
                    <seg corresp="#KR2p0085_tls_001-9a.1" xml:lang="en">If the five capital punishments are not enacted, </seg>
               <seg corresp="#KR2p0085_tls_001-9a.2" xml:lang="en">the people can share what is left over with each other [=live in peace] </seg>
               <seg corresp="#KR2p0085_tls_001-9a.3" xml:lang="en">If for three years no grain grows, </seg>
               <seg corresp="#KR2p0085_tls_001-9a.4" xml:lang="en">(and yet) for five years there are no people feeling cold and hungry, </seg>
               <seg corresp="#KR2p0085_tls_001-9a.5" xml:lang="en">this [...] goodness. </seg>
                </p>

            <p>
                    <seg corresp="#KR2p0085_tls_001-10a.1" xml:lang="en">King Wen said: </seg>
               <seg corresp="#KR2p0085_tls_001-10a.2" xml:lang="en">"I pray [...] </seg>
               <seg corresp="#KR2p0085_tls_001-10a.3" xml:lang="en">??? </seg>
               <seg corresp="#KR2p0085_tls_001-10a.4" xml:lang="en">King Wen asked: </seg>
               <seg corresp="#KR2p0085_tls_001-10a.5" xml:lang="en">"is there a core point in the (pursuit of) proper way?" </seg>
               <seg corresp="#KR2p0085_tls_001-10a.6" xml:lang="en">The august father said: </seg>
               <seg corresp="#KR2p0085_tls_001-10a.7" xml:lang="en">"To respect others and approach the proper way, </seg>
               <seg corresp="#KR2p0085_tls_001-10a.8" xml:lang="en">one should not enact things by himself but to trust [...] </seg>
               <seg corresp="#KR2p0085_tls_001-10a.9" xml:lang="en">therefore using generals (?) ?? </seg>
                </p>

            <p>
                    <seg corresp="#KR2p0085_tls_001-11a.1" xml:lang="en">King Wen said: </seg>
               <seg corresp="#KR2p0085_tls_001-11a.2" xml:lang="en">"May I ask its [...] </seg>
               <seg corresp="#KR2p0085_tls_001-11a.3" xml:lang="en">The august father then said: </seg>
               <seg corresp="#KR2p0085_tls_001-11a.4" xml:lang="en">Now, the first four emperors, </seg>
               <seg corresp="#KR2p0085_tls_001-11a.5" xml:lang="en">the two rulers of [...] </seg>
               <seg corresp="#KR2p0085_tls_001-11a.6" xml:lang="en">(Emperor) Qi established the five laws, </seg>
               <seg corresp="#KR2p0085_tls_001-11a.7" xml:lang="en">Tang the three acts (?)." </seg>
                </p>

            <p>
                    <seg corresp="#KR2p0085_tls_001-12a.1" xml:lang="en">King Wen asked: </seg>
               <seg corresp="#KR2p0085_tls_001-12a.2" xml:lang="en">"The proper way can be sheltered?" </seg>
               <seg corresp="#KR2p0085_tls_001-12a.3" xml:lang="en">The august father said: </seg>
               <seg corresp="#KR2p0085_tls_001-12a.4" xml:lang="en">"The auspicious and luminous Yellow Emperor, </seg>
               <seg corresp="#KR2p0085_tls_001-12a.5" xml:lang="en">Yao [...] </seg>
                </p>

            <p>
                    <seg corresp="#KR2p0085_tls_001-13a.1" xml:lang="en">[...] ?. </seg>
               <seg corresp="#KR2p0085_tls_001-13a.2" xml:lang="en">The august father said: </seg>
               <seg corresp="#KR2p0085_tls_001-13a.3" xml:lang="en">"The Yellow Emperor reformed the three officials (?) </seg>
               <seg corresp="#KR2p0085_tls_001-13a.4" xml:lang="en">[...] don't know its most important point." </seg>
                </p>

            <p>
                    <seg corresp="#KR2p0085_tls_001-14a.1" xml:lang="en">King Wen asked: </seg>
               <seg corresp="#KR2p0085_tls_001-14a.2" xml:lang="en">"???" </seg>
               <seg corresp="#KR2p0085_tls_001-14a.3" xml:lang="en">The august father said: </seg>
               <seg corresp="#KR2p0085_tls_001-14a.4" xml:lang="en">"The Yellow Emperor reformed the three officials, </seg>
               <seg corresp="#KR2p0085_tls_001-14a.5" xml:lang="en">controlled the operations of heaven (日行=天行?) (?), </seg>
               <seg corresp="#KR2p0085_tls_001-14a.6" xml:lang="en">practiced not-knowing </seg>
               <seg corresp="#KR2p0085_tls_001-14a.7" xml:lang="en">established and unified (?) the regulations (?), </seg>
               <seg corresp="#KR2p0085_tls_001-14a.8" xml:lang="en"> </seg>
               <seg corresp="#KR2p0085_tls_001-14a.9" xml:lang="en"> </seg>
                </p>

            <p>
                    <seg corresp="#KR2p0085_tls_001-15a.1" xml:lang="en">[...] asked about the operations of heaven (?). </seg>
               <seg corresp="#KR2p0085_tls_001-15a.2" xml:lang="en">The august father said: </seg>
               <seg corresp="#KR2p0085_tls_001-15a.3" xml:lang="en">"the operations of heaven (?), </seg>
               <seg corresp="#KR2p0085_tls_001-15a.4" xml:lang="en">they are used to bring (things) to completion (?), </seg>
               <seg corresp="#KR2p0085_tls_001-15a.5" xml:lang="en">and their latent ability is accomplished (?), </seg>
               <seg corresp="#KR2p0085_tls_001-15a.6" xml:lang="en">in their proximity they make the masses harmonious (?), </seg>
               <seg corresp="#KR2p0085_tls_001-15a.7" xml:lang="en">at a distance they make for an early achievement (?), </seg>
               <seg corresp="#KR2p0085_tls_001-15a.8" xml:lang="en">these are the operations of heaven (?)." </seg>
                </p>

            <p>
                    <seg corresp="#KR2p0085_tls_001-16a.1" xml:lang="en">As for Yao ruling over all under Heaven, </seg>
               <seg corresp="#KR2p0085_tls_001-16a.2" xml:lang="en">he subdued those revolting against him, </seg>
               <seg corresp="#KR2p0085_tls_001-16a.3" xml:lang="en">always frugal and enlightened, </seg>
               <seg corresp="#KR2p0085_tls_001-16a.4" xml:lang="en">enacting the four [...] </seg>
                </p>

            <p>
                    <seg corresp="#KR2p0085_tls_001-17a.1" xml:lang="en">He enquired about it from the master, </seg>
               <seg corresp="#KR2p0085_tls_001-17a.2" xml:lang="en">saying: </seg>
               <seg corresp="#KR2p0085_tls_001-17a.3" xml:lang="en">"What is the priority in government?" </seg>
               <seg corresp="#KR2p0085_tls_001-17a.4" xml:lang="en">Yu answered: </seg>
               <seg corresp="#KR2p0085_tls_001-17a.5" xml:lang="en">"Intent." </seg>
               <seg corresp="#KR2p0085_tls_001-17a.6" xml:lang="en">Yao [...] </seg>
                </p>

            <p>
                    <seg corresp="#KR2p0085_tls_001-18a.1" xml:lang="en">[...] then creatures are born, </seg>
               <seg corresp="#KR2p0085_tls_001-18a.2" xml:lang="en">from unruliness (?) comes wisdom, </seg>
               <seg corresp="#KR2p0085_tls_001-18a.3" xml:lang="en">heavy metal doesn't flow, </seg>
               <seg corresp="#KR2p0085_tls_001-18a.4" xml:lang="en">jade is not overcome (?) ?? </seg>
                </p>

            <p>
                    <seg corresp="#KR2p0085_tls_001-19a.1" xml:lang="en">Yao had not yet put an end to the chaos of the four harms. </seg>
               <seg corresp="#KR2p0085_tls_001-19a.2" xml:lang="en">Then he asked Yu: </seg>
               <seg corresp="#KR2p0085_tls_001-19a.3" xml:lang="en">"Once the great harms will have been put under control, </seg>
               <seg corresp="#KR2p0085_tls_001-19a.4" xml:lang="en">small [...] </seg>
                </p>

            <p>
                    <seg corresp="#KR2p0085_tls_001-20a.1" xml:lang="en">What is the priority while sitting (quietly- not acting?/seizing time?)? </seg>
               <seg corresp="#KR2p0085_tls_001-20a.2" xml:lang="en">He said: </seg>
               <seg corresp="#KR2p0085_tls_001-20a.3" xml:lang="en">"Do not forget what you are unable to do." </seg>
               <seg corresp="#KR2p0085_tls_001-20a.4" xml:lang="en">Yao said: </seg>
               <seg corresp="#KR2p0085_tls_001-20a.5" xml:lang="en">"Alas!" </seg>
               <seg corresp="#KR2p0085_tls_001-20a.6" xml:lang="en">The vanishing course of time (?), </seg>
               <seg corresp="#KR2p0085_tls_001-20a.7" xml:lang="en">the years coming to an end (?) [...] </seg>
               <seg corresp="#KR2p0085_tls_001-20a.8" xml:lang="en">He inquired (?) about it from Yao, </seg>
               <seg corresp="#KR2p0085_tls_001-20a.9" xml:lang="en">Yao started employing this precious virtue </seg>
                </p>

            <p>
                    <seg corresp="#KR2p0085_tls_001-21a.1" xml:lang="en">As for Shun ruling all under heaven, </seg>
               <seg corresp="#KR2p0085_tls_001-21a.2" xml:lang="en">when the Three Mao did not submit to him, </seg>
               <seg corresp="#KR2p0085_tls_001-21a.3" xml:lang="en">Shun did not change his way, </seg>
               <seg corresp="#KR2p0085_tls_001-21a.4" xml:lang="en">did not obstruct his [...] </seg>
                </p>

            <p>
                    <seg corresp="#KR2p0085_tls_001-22a.1" xml:lang="en">[...] said: </seg>
               <seg corresp="#KR2p0085_tls_001-22a.2" xml:lang="en">"to cultivate government surely (the essential) resides in growing (?), </seg>
               <seg corresp="#KR2p0085_tls_001-22a.3" xml:lang="en">ask [...] </seg>
               <seg corresp="#KR2p0085_tls_001-22a.4" xml:lang="en">lose, </seg>
               <seg corresp="#KR2p0085_tls_001-22a.5" xml:lang="en">(someone) feeling painful to share it with the masses, </seg>
               <seg corresp="#KR2p0085_tls_001-22a.6" xml:lang="en">is not one who is able to harmonize (one's) virtue with the world, </seg>
               <seg corresp="#KR2p0085_tls_001-22a.7" xml:lang="en">[...] when one is enlightened then he protects the state, </seg>
               <seg corresp="#KR2p0085_tls_001-22a.8" xml:lang="en">he recognizes talent and sets the government straight, </seg>
               <seg corresp="#KR2p0085_tls_001-22a.9" xml:lang="en">he teaches beautiful things and then the people comply. </seg>
                </p>

            <p>
                    <seg corresp="#KR2p0085_tls_001-23a.1" xml:lang="en">As for Yu ruling all under Heaven, </seg>
               <seg corresp="#KR2p0085_tls_001-23a.2" xml:lang="en">the submission was deep and everlasting (+-) [...] </seg>
               <seg corresp="#KR2p0085_tls_001-23a.3" xml:lang="en">After five years all under Heaven was corrected. </seg>
               <seg corresp="#KR2p0085_tls_001-23a.4" xml:lang="en">One said: </seg>
               <seg corresp="#KR2p0085_tls_001-23a.5" xml:lang="en">"When Yu served Yao, </seg>
               <seg corresp="#KR2p0085_tls_001-23a.6" xml:lang="en">there was a great flood under heaven. </seg>
                </p>

            <p>
                    <seg corresp="#KR2p0085_tls_001-24a.1" xml:lang="en">Yao then approached Yu saying: </seg>
               <seg corresp="#KR2p0085_tls_001-24a.2" xml:lang="en">"I beg you to go </seg>
               <seg corresp="#KR2p0085_tls_001-24a.3" xml:lang="en">to dredge the rivers and open up the valleys </seg>
               <seg corresp="#KR2p0085_tls_001-24a.4" xml:lang="en">to channel all under heaven." </seg>
                </p>

            <p>
                    <seg corresp="#KR2p0085_tls_001-25a.1" xml:lang="en">Yu dredged the Jiang and made (divided) it into three </seg>
               <seg corresp="#KR2p0085_tls_001-25a.2" xml:lang="en">he dredged the He and divided it into nine </seg>
               <seg corresp="#KR2p0085_tls_001-25a.3" xml:lang="en">the hundred rivers all flowed (freely) </seg>
               <seg corresp="#KR2p0085_tls_001-25a.4" xml:lang="en">he set up 90 key (control) points </seg>
               <seg corresp="#KR2p0085_tls_001-25a.5" xml:lang="en">he excavated three hundred channels </seg>
               <seg corresp="#KR2p0085_tls_001-25a.6" xml:lang="en">His head wrinkled and darkened, his body scaly (?) and coarse. </seg>
                </p>

            <p>
                    <seg corresp="#KR2p0085_tls_001-26a.1" xml:lang="en">Yu made the people doubly harmonious </seg>
               <seg corresp="#KR2p0085_tls_001-26a.2" xml:lang="en">and the people exerted themselves to the utmost </seg>
               <seg corresp="#KR2p0085_tls_001-26a.3" xml:lang="en">the one hundred rivers had been made to flow freely </seg>
               <seg corresp="#KR2p0085_tls_001-26a.4" xml:lang="en">and all under Heaven could be made constant </seg>
                </p>

            <p>
                    <seg corresp="#KR2p0085_tls_001-27a.1" xml:lang="en">"in receiving (orders) from Shun he followed virtue </seg>
               <seg corresp="#KR2p0085_tls_001-27a.2" xml:lang="en">and implemented (it) in the four countries (=everywhere) </seg>
               <seg corresp="#KR2p0085_tls_001-27a.3" xml:lang="en">he thereby instructed the toiling the people </seg>
               <seg corresp="#KR2p0085_tls_001-27a.4" xml:lang="en">and people from all corners exerted themselves to the utmost </seg>
               <seg corresp="#KR2p0085_tls_001-27a.5" xml:lang="en">he strove for balance with anxious intent </seg>
               <seg corresp="#KR2p0085_tls_001-27a.6" xml:lang="en">he was desired and not opposed </seg>
               <seg corresp="#KR2p0085_tls_001-27a.7" xml:lang="en">deep, earnest, strong and abundant (in virtues) </seg>
               <seg corresp="#KR2p0085_tls_001-27a.8" xml:lang="en">he had accomplishments and did not waste (them). </seg>
               <seg corresp="#KR2p0085_tls_001-27a.9" xml:lang="en"> </seg>
                </p>

            <p>
                    <seg corresp="#KR2p0085_tls_001-28a.1" xml:lang="en">A third one said: </seg>
               <seg corresp="#KR2p0085_tls_001-28a.2" xml:lang="en">"When Yu ruled on all under Heaven </seg>
               <seg corresp="#KR2p0085_tls_001-28a.3" xml:lang="en">he made his intent bright </seg>
               <seg corresp="#KR2p0085_tls_001-28a.4" xml:lang="en">and acted unselfishly [...] </seg>
               <seg corresp="#KR2p0085_tls_001-28a.5" xml:lang="en">when he abandoned the body (he died) </seg>
               <seg corresp="#KR2p0085_tls_001-28a.6" xml:lang="en">[one could say of him that] in life he acted so that the people toiled (to their best abilities) </seg>
               <seg corresp="#KR2p0085_tls_001-28a.7" xml:lang="en">in death he acted so that he would not receive sacrifices [=showing utmost modesty] </seg>
               <seg corresp="#KR2p0085_tls_001-28a.8" xml:lang="en">in his youth he acted so that he completed a grand work </seg>
               <seg corresp="#KR2p0085_tls_001-28a.9" xml:lang="en">in his middle age he acted so that he consolidated what was shared (by the people) </seg>
               <seg corresp="#KR2p0085_tls_001-28a.10" xml:lang="en">in his old age he acted so that he did not exhausted [...] </seg>
                </p>

         </div>
      </body>
   </text>
